Package gw.api.metric

Class EditableMetricLimitValue

java.lang.Object
gw.api.metric.EditableMetricLimitValue
public class EditableMetricLimitValue extends Object
Represents a metric limit value in a form that can be displayed by the special MetricLimitValueInput. The value can be integer, decimal, a percentage or currency, according to the type of the metric limit.
